From Rod Sprattling Subject Re Kawi Zephyr was Re Vision vs GpZ In article A , writes In A Erik Asphaug x writes By the way, the short lived Zephyr is essentially a GpZ , Why was the Zephyr discontinued I heard something about a problem with the name, but I never did hear anything certain Ford had an anemic mid sized car by that name back in the last decade I rented one once That car would ruin the name Zephyr for any other use Rod Roderick Sprattling No job too great, no time too small With feet to fire and back to wall